      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "A strike showing huge chunks of\nsteel-galena was made at the Stewart\nmine near Wardner recently. Lawyer\nII. F. samuels. president and man\nager of the mine. brought some rare\nspecimens to the city. The strike was\nmade in the lower 600-foot crosscut\ntunnel. The vein, not yet crosscut,\nshows two feet of solid ore. In the\nupper workings considerable rich car\nDonate ores have been blocked out."
